	Function ReCalculateDestinationDiskAndPartition ( bRequired ) 

		Dim sDriveLetter
		Dim oDiskPart
		Dim bDiskPartFound

		' We may wish to use some advanced Disk Partitioning Routines from ZTIDIskPart.vbs. Check availabiltiy.
